        "Description": "May 6, 2012, 8:35 PM, Stockholm, Sweden and Čadca, Slovakia. Good evening 47, your targets are now Kurt Donovan, Dalia Margolis and Viktor Novikov. After you eliminate Kurt Donovan, Activate code 17 lockdown, then eliminate Dalia Margolis and Viktor Novikov in accident (falling object). After you eliminate 2 remaining targets, phone Mária Pietrová and answer a question about Paul correctly for €33. Good luck 47!\rSources:\rhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HEC884J2Gq0",
